March 12,2020.

Lunar February 19.

The 50th day of the city closure in Wuhan.

The Gates of Heaven are sealed, Day forty-nine.

To tell you the truth, yesterday's message board article made me cringe, and I still went to bed wondering if I was going to wake up the next morning with a 404. Fortunately, the network management, unexpectedly inexplicable Xi mention life second 10w + , mixed feelings. From the point of view of communication, I "planned to succeed" ; but from the point of view of communication environment, this is undoubtedly a satire and a dirge. As Liao Xinzhong said at the end of his essay yesterday, "the absurd comedy inspired by this essay is also a perfect illustration of the core of comedy, which is a tragedy. "

Environment on the first do not complain, from the point of view of communication, why in the many relay articles, I survived and harvest 10w + experience it. Unlike the last 10w + , which didn't make sense, this time there was a bit of planning ahead. The first is a whistle-blower (hot spot) -- but it's also a hot whistle, and if you don't catch it, you blow yourself up. After having sacrificed so many variants to spread the article, it is hard to break out of it with a new variant. Yeah, well, I'm not really educated, so I can't make up a great genre like that. Also have thought of doing a collection directly, but slowly see to do a collection of the number is also more (homogenization) . To return to the essence of the problem, first, to relay the dissemination of this article, second, to solve the problem of dissemination by 404; then the most important, the text should be standardized without error, the message we do not see the same? So decided to use the message as an article dissemination carrier. (differentiation)

First, I was going to go it alone, and then I thought, well, isn't this just an opportunity for everyone to be active in making their voices heard? So in the circle of friends and groups issued a co-build Message Board Call, and soon there are 20 or 30 enthusiastic partners to respond. But there was still a gap between the 100 messages I had imagined, so I kept up the call and finally got the full number in the afternoon. After all, the rough-and-tumble team, in the first paragraph of the article to change the nickname of the sign, they are faced with the situation of someone not online, very head-splitting. Specifically in the message process, there are I thoughtless, on the order of the message impact of reading this article the biggest variable concern. However, I was surprised to find that under the active interaction of the vast number of enthusiastic netizens, I had almost straightened out the message articles. This is also the most gratifying and gratifying part. She said she watched it almost in tears, as angry and heartbroken as I was, as proud as I am that we have so many good people, and as angry as we are that we can not speak.

It was supposed to be a flash mob performance art, but it ended up causing a little splash. I am very grateful to you for your participation, the group cleared away some of the bustle, left behind are quite cherish the network of the fate of a line. So if you also want to come in"make a mess of things", welcome to reply in the backstage signal"whistle", can jump into group link, also can add me to pull you directly. In winter, let's huddle together for warmth.
